<li>The default configuration now features lots more actions mapped to the Middle Button. Namely ‚ÄòLook Up‚Äô, ‚ÄòShow Desktop‚Äô, ‚ÄòLaunchpad‚Äô, and ‚ÄòMission Control &amp; Spaces‚Äô. I think that, with the new cleaned-up layout, this is not overwhelming to new users like it would have been with the old layout. It teaches users about the possibilities and it empowers users who don‚Äôt like to spend much time setting things up.</li>
